snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 4092 | 23 May 2024 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4092: Dono Parties Mein Hua Jhagda
--------------------------------------------------------
Kurmura Kumar insists that Gokuldham members keep the buttermilk stall running. Meanwhile, Taarak's boss discovers his deception and his lemonade sales. Conflict ensues as Kurmura Kumar's and Chana Kumar's factions clash over the drinks, leading to a chaotic brawl.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4092 | 23 May 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1000275589

snippet.title: Prashant Kishor's Bold Prediction For 2024 Lok Sabha Elections
snippet.description:
#prashantkishor #loksabhaelections2024 #pmmodi #ndaalliance #indialliance 
Join Business Today's Executive Director Rahul Kanwal in an exclusive conversation with renowned political analyst Prashant Kishor as they delve into the 2024 Lok Sabha poll predictions. Prashant Kishor forecasts that the BJP is poised to secure around 300 seats in the upcoming elections. Kishor dismisses the possibility of the BJP winning 370 seats, as recently claimed by Prime Minister Narendra Modi, calling it motivational rhetoric rather than a realistic goal. He emphasizes that while surpassing 370 seats is improbable, the BJP is also unlikely to drop below 270 seats. According to Kishor, the BJP's performance in the 2024 elections is expected to be on par with the previous Lok Sabha results, potentially achieving around 303 seats or slightly more. Tune in to this insightful discussion to gain a deeper understanding of the political landscape as the nation approaches the crucial 2024 elections. 400 paar? BJP out? Or struggle for 272? As election fever peaks, political strategist Prashant Kishor shares his insights on the current state of play. Kishor talks of the vulnerabilities that have built up over 10 years of the Modi government, what to expect from Modi 3.0, and why he thinks there will be many more street protests over the next five years than in the past decade. Kishor’s also betting his reputation and future on being able to win the Bihar assembly elections in 2025.
-----------------------

snippet.title: Thank you 6 Million Friends | Chef Alandra's Chocolate Cake Recipe in Tamil
snippet.description:
Our Madras Samayal family has now grown to 60 lakh subscribers and we are now a family of 6 million friends. I thank you for you all for your love and support over all these years. Your positive feedback and encouraging comments have enabled me to continue this journey. I am so proud to be part of this family and thank you for providing me this opportunity to share the love of cooking with you.
#chocolatecake #cakerecipeintamil 

 To celebrate this special occasion chef Alandra will be making an ultra moist chocolate cake recipe. Please do try this cake recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. This chocolate cake is perfect for all celebratory occasions. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!



Ingredients:
For the ultra moist Chocolate cake recipe:
3 Eggs
1/2 cup Milk (125 ml)
1/2 cup Curd (125 ml)
1/2 cup Oil (125 ml)
1/4 cup melted Butter (25g)
2-3 tsp Vanilla extract
1.5 cup Sugar (300g)
1.5 cup Maida (185g)
1/2 cup Cocoa powder (50g)
1.5 tsp Baking powder
3/4 tsp Baking Soda
1/4 tsp Salt
Bake at 175C /350 F for 35-38 min (8*8 inch square pan)

For the Chocolate frosting:

1/2 cup cream 
1 cup semi sweet chocolate chips (150g)
2 tbsp Butter
50g powdered Sugar (can increase up to 75 g to suit our preference)
If using  dark chocolate increase the amount of powdered Sugar
If using  Milk Chocolate only 2 tbsp of powdered Sugar would be sufficient.

2-3 tsp Vanilla extract
1.5 cup Sugar (300g)
1.5 cup Maida (185g)
1/2 cup Cocoa powder (50g)
1.5 tsp Baking powder
3/4 tsp Baking Soda
1/4 tsp Salt
Bake at 175C /350 F for 35-38 min (8*8 inch square pan)

For the Chocolate frosting:

1/2 cup cream 
1 cup semi sweet chocolate chips (150g)
2 tbsp Butter
50g powdered Sugar (can increase up to 75 g to suit our preference)
If using  dark chocolate increase the amount of powdered Sugar
If using  Milk Chocolate only 2 tbsp of powdered Sugar would be sufficient.

en.title: Thank you 6 Million Friends | Chef Alandra's Chocolate Cake Recipe in Tamil
en.description:
Our Madras Samayal family has now grown to 60 lakh subscribers and we are now a family of 6 million friends. I thank you for you all for your love and support over all these years. Your positive feedback and encouraging comments have enabled me to continue this journey. I am so proud to be part of this family and thank you for providing me this opportunity to share the love of cooking with you.
#chocolatecake #cakerecipeintamil 

 To celebrate this special occasion chef Alandra will be making an ultra moist chocolate cake recipe. Please do try this cake recipe at home and share it with your friends and family. This chocolate cake is perfect for all celebratory occasions. Also, please do share your feedback about the recipe in the comments below. All the best and happy cooking!



Ingredients:
For the ultra moist Chocolate cake recipe:
3 Eggs
1/2 cup Milk (125 ml)
1/2 cup Curd (125 ml)
1/2 cup Oil (125 ml)
1/4 cup melted Butter (25g)
2-3 tsp Vanilla extract
1.5 cup Sugar (300g)
1.5 cup Maida (185g)
1/2 cup Cocoa powder (50g)
1.5 tsp Baking powder
3/4 tsp Baking Soda
1/4 tsp Salt
Bake at 175C /350 F for 35-38 min (8*8 inch square pan)

For the Chocolate frosting:

1/2 cup cream 
1 cup semi sweet chocolate chips (150g)
2 tbsp Butter
50g powdered Sugar (can increase up to 75 g to suit our preference)
If using  dark chocolate increase the amount of powdered Sugar
If using  Milk Chocolate only 2 tbsp of powdered Sugar would be sufficient.

snippet.title: Girls In Parallel Universe | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys 
This Video shows different scenarios of Girls in Parallel Universe . How the world will be if there is role reversal girls behaved like boys and boys acted like girls , universe would be so different . Scenes like wife going on job and husband packing lunch for her , girls acting like guys and eve teasing boys on street , shadi rishta and dowry , politicians during elections making policies for boys , brave sisters rescuing their brothers , world where period leave and pregnancy leave persists , girl things and struggles becomes boy things and boy struggles . Sister after college catching brother at cafe marrying him off and not letting him continue his studies , so many more fun and relatable points  , you will love it and Relate with this video.. Enjoy and laugh out loud. 

This video is filled with  memories and situations we all have been in . 
Relish and Relive those fun moments
Do share it with your friends and family , Relatives , Neighbour  .. Comment down your Fav Part ,

snippet.title: ALERT! #1 SECRET KILLER killing more people than COVID
snippet.description:

NEET Magic 2025 Course - https://www.neetwale.com/learn/NEET-MAGIC-2025 
NEET Magic 2026 Course - https://www.neetwale.com/learn/NEET-MAGIC-2026 

The Air Quality Index of India is in an alarming condition. Out of the top 50 most polluted cities, 42 are Indian cities… Delhi sitting right at the top! 
The AQI index measures the amount of pollutants in the air and the scale expands till 500. But a recent survey revealed Delhi had crossed 900 mark, that isn’t even measured by the scale, just imagine! There are so many experiments proving that if you live in any of the top Indian metropolitan cities and you still haven’t smoked a cigarette… Well, not a big deal, your lungs might still be as damaged as of a serial smokers’.
There are many reasons behind the low AQI of India, but we can do 2 things about it!
1- Sit and wait for the govt to take action
2- Take matters into our own hands, spread awareness on this issue and try and save ourselves!

snippet.title: 25 ஆயிரம் ஆண்களுக்கு படைக்கப்பட்ட மெகா கிடா கறி விருந்து 🔥😲Karumparai Muthaiya Temple -  Madurai
snippet.description:
Madurai Karumparai Muthaiyah Temple Kari Virunthu 

மதுரை கரும்பாறை முத்தையா கோவில் அசைவ திருவிழா !!! 

25 ஆயிரம் ஆண்களுக்கு படைத்த மெகா கறி விருந்து !!


மதுரை மாவட்டம் திருமங்கலம் அருகே உள்ள அனுப்பபட்டி கிராமம் உள்ளது. இங்கு காவல் தெய்வமான கரும்பாறை முத்தையா கோயில் உள்ளது. இந்த கோயிலில் பல ஆண்டுகளாக மார்கழி மாதம் ஆண்கள் மட்டுமே பங்கேற்கும் திருவிழா பாரம்பரியமாக நடந்து வருகிறது. இந்த திருவிழாவில் பிறந்த பெண் குழந்தை முதல் வயதான மூதாட்டி வரையிலான பெண்கள் பங்கேற்க அனுமதி கிடையாது.

இந்த விழாவில் பலியிடப்படும் ஆடுகள் கோயிலிலேயே வளர்க்கப்படுகின்றன. கோவிலில் வளரும் இந்த ஆடுகள் மேய்ச்சலுக்காக அருகில் உள்ள வயல் மற்றும் விளைநிலங்களில் உணவை தேடி செல்லும் போது அந்த ஆடுகளை யாரும் விரட்டமாட்டார்கள். முத்தையா சாமியே வந்து தங்களது வயலில் இரை தேடுவதாக நம்பிக்கை வைத்துள்ளனர். இந்த ஆண்டு கரும்பாறை முத்தையா கோயில் திருவிழா வெகு விமர்சையாக  நடந்தது.


காலை 8 மணிக்கு பொங்கல் வைத்து வழிபாட்டை துவக்கினர். பின்னர், நேர்த்திக் கடனாக செலுத்தப்பட்ட 90 ஆடுகள் பலியிடப்பட்டு உணவாக சமைக்கப்பட்டன. 50 மூடை அரிசியில் சாதம் தயாரானது. கரும்பாறை முத்தையா சுவாமிக்கு உருவம் கிடையாததால் அங்கு சமைக்கப்பட்ட அன்னத்தை மலை போல் குவித்து பிறகு கறி குழம்பு எடுத்து வந்து அன்னத்தில் படைத்து சிறப்பு பூஜைகள் நடைபெற்றது. அதனைத் தொடர்ந்து அண்டாக்களில் தயாராக இருந்த கறி குழம்பு கறிகளை மட்டும் தனியாக பிரித்து ஒரு இடத்தில் மொத்தமாக கொட்டி வைத்து விடுவார்கள்.

 முதலில் கறியை வைத்து அதன் பின் சாதம், அதன் பின் கறி குழம்பு ஊற்றி அன்னதானம் நடைபெறும். இந்த கறி விருந்து அங்கு கூடியிருந்த சுமார் 25 ஆயிரத்திற்கும் மேற்பட்ட ஆண்களுக்கு வழங்கப்பட்டது. இலை போட்டு சாதமும், ஆட்டுகறி குழம்பும் ஆண்களுக்கு பிரசாதமாக பறிமாறப்பட்டது. சாப்பிட்ட பிறகு இலையை எடுக்காமல் அப்படியே விட்டுச் செல்வது வழக்கம்.

இந்த இலைகள் காய்ந்து, அங்கிருந்து மறைந்த பிறகே பெண்கள் கோயிலுக்கு தரிசனத்திற்கு வருவர். மே 18 அன்று  நடந்த கறிவிருந்தில் திருமங்கலம், கரடிக்கல், மாவிலிபட்டி, செக்காணூரணி, சோழவந்தான் உள்ளிட்ட பல்வேறு பகுதிகளைச் சேர்ந்த ஆயிரக்கணக்கான ஆண்கள் கலந்து கொண்டனர். அடுத்த ஆண்டு அன்னதான விழாவிற்காக பக்தர்கள் இப்போதே நேர்த்திக் கடனாக ஆடுகளை வழங்கினர். நேர்த்தி கடனாக வழங்கப்படும் ஆடுகள் கருப்பு ஆடுகளாக மட்டுமே வழங்க வேண்டும் என்பது குறிப்பிடத்தக்கது.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Chand Bargi Ae Tu Tanne Lyau Ke Mai Taare
Je Galti Te Madam Ji Bannjo Hamare
Ram Ki Syu Gabru Ne Aajenge Nazaare 

Tere Laare Mai Bhi Yo Pyaar Tove Nakhro

Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ek Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro

Gabru Ne Haaye Tera Moh Itna
Jnu Aave Se Kisaan Ne Zameen Ka
Chaar Mein Te 3 Din Kattjawange 
Haseen Scene Bna Gel Coffee Peen Ka
Zulf Aankhya Te Jadd Dekhe Tu Htaake
Aaja Se Swaad Fer Jeen Ka
Gali Ke Me Tere Chora Maare Jaawe Gede
Kaam Hoya Pda Mera Yo Routine Ka 

Teri Rakh Sirhaane Photo Chora Sove Nakhroo

Ik Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ik Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro
Ik Teri Haan.... Na Hove Nakhro

Dikhe Je Sveree Chori Laage Tu Gulaab 
Ar Saanj Ne Tu Chadde Se Sharaab Si
Baawla Sa Hoya Tere Paache Sisaraala
Roz Khyaalan Mein Tu Bann Aave Khwaab Si 
Barainnn Hotthan Te Konya Chup Todti
Laage Koi Bann Tu Kitaab Si 
Chore Ne Ishaare Pe Tu Krawe Salsa
Haan Krke Khatam Kr Baat Si

Kyu Beej Bignn Ke Tu Nyu Bove Nakhroo..

snippet.title: Agar Ho Tum | Mr. & Mrs. Mahi | Rajkummar Rao, Janhvi Kapoor | Tanishk B., Jubin N., Kausar M.
snippet.description:
Hai tera, hai mera, humara ye saara jahaan! 
Presenting the second song from ‘Mr. and Mrs. Mahi’, ‘Agar Ho Tum’ is composed by Tanishk Bagchi. Penned by Kausar Munir and sung by Jubin Nautiyal, the magical song features Rajkummar Rao and Janhvi Kapoor in it.

#AgarHoTum #RajkummarRao #JanhviKapoor #MrandMrsMahi 

Composer - Tanishk Bagchi 
Singer - Jubin Nautiyal 
Chorus: Sudhanshu Shome , Rakesh Deol, Pankaj Dixit, Anupam Barman
Lyricist - Kausar Munir
Guitars - Shomu Seal
Song Recorded by Abhishek Khandelwal at YRF Studios
Dholak - Raju Sardar & Hafeez Ahmed Khan
Tabla - Sanjiv Sen 
Music Producer - Tanishk Bagchi 
Music Supervisor - Azeem Dayani
Associate Music Supervisor – Manish Natekar
Mixing And Mastering - Eric Pillai @ Future Sound of Bombay 
Mix Assistant Engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai 
Special Thanks - Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Digital promotion - Net Media (Sagar Saroha)

Mr. & Mrs. Mahi in cinemas 31st May

Zee Studios & Dharma Productions present
A Dharma Productions film
MR. & MRS. MAHI
Starring Rajkummar Rao and Janhvi Kapoor
Directed by Sharan Sharma
Produced by Karan Johar, Zee Studios, Hiroo Yash Johar & Apoorva Mehta
Written by Nikhil Mehrotra & Sharan Sharma
A Zee Studios Worldwide release

Lyrics: 

Agar ho tum toh
Main khud ko bhula doon,
Tere khwaabon, khayaalon mein, yun hi main behta rahoon...

Agar ho tum toh
Hai phir kehna kya,
Tere vaadon, iraadon mein yun hi main uddhta rahoon...

Zamaane bhar ki khushiyon ko,
Tere daaman mein bhar doonga,
Tu maange ek sitaara
Chaand main tere haath mein rakh doonga!

Agar ho tum,
Toh darrna kya haan,
Hai tera, hai mera, humara ye saara jahaan...

Agar ho tum,
Toh saath khuda haan,
Hai tera, hai mera, humara ye saara jahaan...

Agar ho tum…
Agar ho tum…

Shiddat Episode 32 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by Cerelac - 21st May 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by Cerelac

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: 3 IDIOTS w/ Kristen & Michael Movie Reaction Part (1/3)! | Aamir Khan | Kareena Kapoor | Madhavan
snippet.description:
Kristen and Michael react to ‘3 Idiots',  an inspiring comedy-drama that takes you on a joyous ride of laughter and lessons. It’s a story of three friends studying in an engineering college and their journey filled with fun, frolic, and profound life lessons.

The movie stars the versatile Aamir Khan (Taare Zameen Par & PK), the dynamic R. Madhavan (Rehnaa Hai Terre Dil Mein & Tanu Weds Manu), the charming Sharman Joshi (Rang De Basanti & Golmaal), and the talented Kareena Kapoor Khan (Jab We Met & Good Newwz). The film is directed by the acclaimed director Rajkumar Hirani, known for his work in ‘Munna Bhai M.B.B.S.’ & ‘PK’.

#3Idiots #AamirKhan #RMadhavan #SharmanJoshi #KareenaKapoorKhan #RajkumarHirani #MovieReaction #BollywoodReaction #ComedyDrama #LifeLessons #IndianCinema

snippet.title: ANSWERING YOUR QUESTIONS ✨ Q & A session ✨
snippet.description:
If vitamin C seems to work for everyone but you, then you have probably been using the wrong products all along. It's tough to find formulas that tame the famously unstable vitamin C, which is barely absorbed in its active form. This is why using concentrated vitamin C serums, like the newly launched Garnier Vitamin C Night Serum, can make all the difference.  
The Garnier Overnight Serum will give you power-packed antioxidants in the potent form of #10%PureVitaminC. Pure and stable, the Garnier Bright Complete #VitaminCNightSerum goes deep inside your skin to repair it at night - the best time for skin repair! Now, you can wake up to brighter skin instantly with this #Brightovernight serum. Enriched with #10%PureVitaminC, the Garnier Night Serum neutralises all the free radicals caused by oxidative stress from UV, pollution, and other aggressors. Using Garnier Overnight Serum reduces oxidative stress by -76% and prevents excess melanin production in your skin. Dodge the dark spots and dullness brought on by these radicals with the Garnier Bright Complete overnight serum, and make things simple for your skin.

With a minimal formula of 12 ingredients, the Garnier Skin Naturals Bright Complete Serum is free from sulphates, parabens, silicones, and alcohol. Suitable for all skin types, the Garnier Overnight Serum arrests your free radicals to give you the glow of your dreams. You can always pair it with the Garnier Bright Complete Day Serum to get complete, round-the-clock vitamin C brightness.

Adding an innate glow to your skin can get tricky. So, I put my bets on the #Brightovernight. Let the Garnier Night Serum do its job while you catch up on your beauty sleep and wake up to bright, even-toned skin.

Thanks a ton, for diving into another skincare gem with me, the #VitaminCNightSerum! As always, show your love and like, share, and subscribe to know more secrets behind glowing skin. And don’t forget to share your thoughts in the comments section below.

Make Garnier Vitamin C Night Serum a part of your skincare routine by clicking on the link below 👇

snippet.title: आम का फ्रेश पना, ट्रेडीशनल तरीके से-सिर्फ एक ग्लास  ठंडक-एनर्जी दे व लू से बचाये । Mango Pana Recipe
snippet.description:
परंपरागत तरीके से बना कच्चे आम का ताज़ा पना. इस चिलचिलाती गर्मी में इसका सिर्फ एक ग्लास शरीर में ठंडक, ताजगी और एनर्जी भर देता है.  लू वगैरह से भी बचाता है.  आपके सारे परिवार के लिये
#mangopanna #shorbet #mangodrink #summerdrink 

Ingredients for Aam Panna
क्च्चा आम - Raw mango - 3 no (450 grams)
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1.5 tbsp
चीनी - Sugar - 3/4 cup
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - 1/2 tsp, roasted
काला नमक - Black salt - 1 tsp
पुदीना पाउडर - Pudina powder - 1/2 tsp

In this uproarious video, Priya and Harsh take an unprecedented step – they sue their parents for denying them permission to go on a Goa trip. What follows is a courtroom battle like no other, filled with quirky arguments, relatable situations, and side-splitting humor.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Shiddat Episode 31 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 20th May 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?
